726
01:18:15,691 --> 01:18:17,725
Da pomažem ljudima.

727
01:18:19,962 --> 01:18:22,529
<i>Ali ponekad te
život satera u ćošak,</i>

728
01:18:23,485 --> 01:18:26,486
